column2: Thinking of our friends @MiamiHEAT & @OrlandoMagic during this time. Our thoughts are with all affected by Hurricane Irma. Stay safe.
column5: ['Thinking of our friends @MiamiHEAT & @OrlandoMagic during this time. Our thoughts are with all affected by Hurricane Irma. Stay safe.', 'Thank you for keeping us and the state of Florida in your thoughts! We appreciate your support during this time.']

column2: Our thoughts and prayers are with the @MiamiHEAT's @ChrisBosh.
column5: ["Our thoughts and prayers are with the @MiamiHEAT's @ChrisBosh.", "@orlandomagic We'd like to thank your organization for sending your well wishes to Chris. We greatly appreciate it."]

column2:
Rivals on the court. Family off the court. Stay safe @MiamiHEAT.

Our thoughts are with all our friends in Florida and the southeast.
column5: ['Rivals on the court. Family off the court. Stay safe @MiamiHEAT.\n\nOur thoughts are with all our friends in Florida and the southeast. ', 'Thank you for keeping us in your thoughts! We wish you all the best up in Central Florida as well. Stay safe this weekend.']

column2: Stay safe @MiamiHEAT. We are thinking of you and your fans!
